                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      -|
| **Family Disagreements**      | Money makes people act in strange ways. If you have siblings or other heirs, you now have business partners you didn't choose. One wants to sell fast, one wants to fix it up, and another wants to move in. It’s a recipe for conflict. We've seen families torn apart over a house.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         