                                                                                                                                                                                      -|
| **The Financial Drain**      | A vacant house is a money pit. You’re on the hook for the mortgage, property taxes (which average 0.86% in Nevada), insurance, utilities, and HOA fees. In Las Vegas, a dead A/C in the summer can lead to bigger problems. Every month you wait, you’re losing money. [3]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     