                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    -|
| **Condition of the Property** | Let’s be honest, the house probably needs work. Maybe it’s just dated with 20-year-old carpet and fixtures. Or maybe it has major issues—a leaky roof, a dead AC unit, or foundation problems. Getting a house “market-ready” can cost a fortune and take months you don’t have. We've seen it all - from polybutylene plumbing to outdated electrical panels.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                